target.comment:
FHIR R5 Resource `ObservationDefinition` is representable via FHIR R4B Resource `ObservationDefinition`.
Element `ObservationDefinition` is mapped to FHIR R4B element `ObservationDefinition`.

FHIR R5 Resource `ObservationDefinition` is representable via FHIR STU3 Resource `Basic`.
